{"word":"Month","slug":"month","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Month</b> Ancient use of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=7&verse=11'>Gen 7:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=8&verse=4'>Gen 8:4</a><br/> Twelve months reckoned to a year<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=15'>1Ch 27:15</a><br/> 1. Abib (April):<br/> - The Jewish calendar began with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=2'>Exo 12:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=4'>Exo 13:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=16&verse=1'>Deu 16:1</a> <br/> - Passover instituted and celebrated in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=28'>Exo 12:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=23&verse=15'>Exo 23:15</a> <br/> - Israelites left Egypt in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=4'>Exo 13:4</a> <br/> - Tabernacle set up in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=2'>Exo 40:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=17'>Exo 40:17</a> <br/> - Israelites arrive at Zin in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=20&verse=1'>Num 20:1</a> <br/> - Cross Jordan in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=4&verse=19'>Jos 4:19</a> <br/> - Jordan overflows in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=15'>1Ch 12:15</a> <br/> - Decree to put the Jews to death in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=3&verse=12'>Est 3:12</a> <br/> - The death of Jesus in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26'>Mat 26</a> <br/> - After the captivity called Nisan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=2&verse=1'>Neh 2:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=3&verse=7'>Est 3:7</a> <br/> 2. Zif (May):<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=1'>1Ki 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=37'>1Ki 6:37</a> <br/> - Israel numbered in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=1'>Num 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=18'>Num 1:18</a> <br/> - Passover to be observed in, by the unclean and others who could not observe it in the first month<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=9&verse=11'>Num 9:11</a> <br/> - Israel departed from the wilderness of Zin in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=11'>Num 10:11</a> <br/> - Temple begun in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=1'>1Ki 6:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=3&verse=2'>2Ch 3:2</a> <br/> - An irregular Passover celebrated in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=30&verse=27'>2Ch 30:27</a> <br/> - Rebuilding of the temple begun in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=8'>Ezr 3:8</a> <br/> 3. Sivan (June):<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=8&verse=9'>Est 8:9</a> <br/> - Asa renews the covenant of himself and people in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=15&verse=10'>2Ch 15:10</a> <br/> 4. Tammuz (July): Mentioned by number, not by name<br/> - Jerusalem taken by Nebuchadnezzar in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=2'>Jer 39:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=7'>Jer 52:7</a> <br/> 5. Ab (August): mentioned by number, not by name<br/> - Aaron died on the first day of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=38'>Num 33:38</a> <br/> - Temple destroyed in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=10'>2Ki 25:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=1&verse=3'>Jer 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=30'>Jer 52:30</a> <br/> - Ezra arrived at Jerusalem in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=7&verse=9'>Ezr 7:9</a> <br/> 6. Elul (September):<br/> - Wall of Jerusalem finished in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=6&verse=15'>Neh 6:15</a> <br/> - Temple built in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=37&chapter=1&verse=15'>Hag 1:15</a> <br/> 7. Ethanim (October):<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=2'>1Ki 8:2</a> <br/> - Feasts held in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=24'>Lev 23:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=23&verse=27'>Lev 23:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=15'>Neh 8:15</a> <br/> - Jubilee proclaimed in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=25&verse=9'>Lev 25:9</a> <br/> - Solomon's temple dedicated in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=2'>1Ki 8:2</a> <br/> - Altar rebuilt and offerings renewed in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=1'>Ezr 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=6'>Ezr 3:6</a> <br/> 8. Bul (November):<br/> - The temple finished in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=6&verse=38'>1Ki 6:38</a> <br/> - Jeroboam's idolatrous feast in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=33'>1Ki 12:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=11'>1Ch 27:11</a> <br/> 9. Chisleu (December):<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=9'>Ezr 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36&verse=9'>Jer 36:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36&verse=22'>Jer 36:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=7&verse=1'>Zec 7:1</a><br/> 10. Tebeth (January):<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=16'>Est 2:16</a> <br/> - Nebuchadnezzar besieges Jerusalem in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=1'>2Ki 25:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=4'>Jer 52:4</a> <br/> 11. Sebat (February):<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=1&verse=7'>Zec 1:7</a> <br/> - Moses probably died in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=3'>Deu 1:3</a> <br/> 12. Adar (March):<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=3&verse=7'>Est 3:7</a> <br/> - Second temple finished in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=6&verse=15'>Ezr 6:15</a> <br/> - Feast of Purim in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=9&verse=26'>Est 9:26</a> <br/> Months in prophecy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=11&verse=2'>Rev 11:2</a>"}]}